               <msContents>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i1">
                     <rubric>Nomina sacra; name of the protagonist; names of the donor and his wife; groups of lines on the incipit page; a few lines of the incipit of all sections; incipit of subsections; elements of the punctuation signs and of the text dividers; elements of Ethiopic numerals.</rubric>
